spec_data.Name: python-tablib
spec_data.Description:
Tablib is a format-agnostic tabular dataset library, written in Python.

Output formats supported:

 - Excel (Sets + Books)
 - JSON (Sets + Books)
 - YAML (Sets + Books)
 - HTML (Sets)
 - TSV (Sets)
 - CSV (Sets)
